metadata.name: Volcalla
metadata.description:
She ran away. Escaped from her past and her present... 
Today there is only this day. Explosive, bright, colorful. Flowing like lava from a volcano, glowing with unreal warm colors. 
She is so full of energy that it lights up everything and everyone. 

At her feet you want to stay forever. 
Just to be near her. Not with her. 
And at the same time to bask in the rays of her energy waves. 

She's here... 
She's here for the long haul... 
She's here for an eternity...
